{"tid":2148766,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男警否認瞞債借貸　稱案情唔係表面咁簡單","createTime":"2020-08-10T05:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T06:01:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1bb26b01c35057995a3266b134a69752b0b031","tid":2148766,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"男警涉嫌3次隱瞞其逾100萬港元的債務，向財務機構申請借貸，被控3項欺詐罪，案件今日（10日）在九龍城法院再訊。被告否認全部控罪，其代表律師表示將同意大部份案情，而爭議點將會是被告是否有意圖欺詐，又形容案件「唔係表面咁簡單，但審訊唔係咁複雜」。法庭排期在11月3日開審，預計審期3日，並准被告繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n46歲被告姚漢萍，在控罪書上並無報稱職業。控罪指，他在2017至2018年期間約10個月內，分別向大新銀行、亞洲聯合財務及大眾財務，隱瞞一筆135萬港元的債務，以致3間公司向他批出共43萬港元的貸款。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 東方"},{"pid":"8e0dab2a7e53d4af9918885bbad89ab9941af088","tid":2148766,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc73a9548a49f5486c2a52612c1b3bf1141a4df0","tid":2148766,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:56:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2972099e318e23893505a5fee638414db653d08d","tid":2148766,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc73a9548a49f5486c2a52612c1b3bf1141a4df0","tid":2148766,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:56:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"平時做政治打手，俾PPRB幫得口多<br />\n而家以為犯啲非政治事件都係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共產黨最撚忌你玩臭佢個「依法治國」既朵"}]}